<p class="XzvDs _208Ie _3_7DB blog-post-text-font blog-post-text-color _2p1aK _158eo _3_7DB" style="text-align: left;">When I asked what resources you wanted me to create to make moving home easier and less stressful for you, t<strong>he biggest response was to have a moving checklist to keep track of everything!</strong> Your wish is my command and like your moving fairy godmother I've waved my magic MacBook and bibbidibobiddibo&nbsp;here it is!</p>
